%N A397715 Self-convolution of hyperfactorials (A002109).
%F A397715 a(n) = Sum_{k=0..n} A002109(k)*A002109(n-k).
%F A397715 a(n) ~ 2*A * n^(n*(n+1)/2 + 1/12) / exp(n^2/4), where A is the Glaisher-Kinkelin constant A074962.
%t A397715 Table[Sum[Hyperfactorial[k]*Hyperfactorial[n-k], {k, 0, n}], {n, 0, 12}]
